data.clean_description: Price per 35 grams 1 / 8 oz. Produced from the fields of the famous Hash producing area of Ketama in the Rif Mountains of Morocco. Soft and oily with a slight bubble with heat applied. Aromatic with a fruity and grassy fragrance when torn apart. A Sweet , earthy spice when smoked. Fully India with good THC and CBD levels making a well balanced stone.
data.name: Morrocan Ketama A grade Rif Hashish 3.5 grams
